com.team23.weather.models

Class CompoundForecast

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.team23.weather.models.CompoundForecast

  • public class CompoundForecast
extends java.lang.Object
    Wraps Forecast to provide a model that contains multiple Forecast objects. This is used to represent the hourly and daily forecasts.
    Author:
    Saquib Mian
